snippet.title: Scarlet Nexus - DLC Pack 2 & Free Update 1.05 Trailer | PS5, PS4
snippet.description:
The Bond Enhancement Pack 2 is coming soon to Scarlet Nexus!

It will include:
🔺 10 new bond episodes
🔺 "Youth Attire" costume & weapon set by Daisuke Richard

And the FREE update v.1.05 will add:
🔺 New Battle Simulator feature
🔺 4 Others variations
🔺 New hooded costumes, weapons & more!
